OL,3,CPlans unveiled for low traffic
OL,4,Cneighbourhood in South Bristol
OL,6,FPlans have been unveiled to create a
OL,7,Flow traffic neighbourhood in South
OL,8,FBristol to stop people taking
OL,9,Fshortcuts through residential streets.
OL,11,FBollards and planters will be
OL,12,Finstalled in certain parts of
OL,13,FBedminster, Southville and Windmill
OL,14,FHill, to reduce traffic.
