OL,3,CPlans unveiled for low traffic
OL,4,Cneighbourhood in South Bristol
OL,6,FGreen Councillor Tony Dyer, council
OL,7,Fleader and representing Southville,
OL,8,Fsaid: "This project is about creating
OL,9,Fbetter neighbourhoods for everyone to
OL,10,Flive in. We want to cut down on rat-
OL,11,Fruns and through-traffic to create
OL,12,Fsafer streets for our children and
OL,13,Fmake it easier and more pleasant to
OL,14,Fwalk and cycle.
OL,16,F"South Bristol Liveable Neighbourhoods
OL,17,Frepresents a huge investment in the
OL,18,Farea, and we want everyone to have a
OL,19,Fsay to help us develop the plans for
OL,20,Fthe next stage."
