OL,3,CPlans unveiled for low traffic
OL,4,Cneighbourhood in South Bristol
OL,6,FDrivers would still be able to access
OL,7,Fevery street in the area by vehicle,
OL,8,Falthough some might have to take
OL,9,Fslightly longer routes.
OL,11,FOther changes could include improving
OL,12,Fpedestrian crossings, planting more
OL,13,Ftrees, installing more benches, and
OL,14,Fupgrading lighting.
OL,16,FThe council hopes that reducing
OL,17,Ftraffic will encourage more people to
OL,18,Fwalk, cycle or scoot around the area
OL,19,Finstead of travelling by car.
