OL,3,CPlans unveiled for low traffic
OL,4,Cneighbourhood in South Bristol
OL,6,FThe consultation will run until 13
OL,7,FOctober and people living in the area
OL,8,Fcan tell the council what they like
OL,9,Fand what they want to improve.
OL,11,FThe East Bristol Liveable
OL,12,FNeighbourhood has proved
OL,13,Fcontroversial, and a trial is expected
OL,14,Fto launch this summer.
OL,16,FMany people living in the area support
OL,17,Fthe plans, particularly due to fears
OL,18,Fover road safety, speeding cars and
OL,19,Ffrequent crashes. But others oppose
OL,20,Fthem due to the increased lengths of
OL,21,Ftheir journeys in a car or van.
